<div>
 <img src="images/aoc.png" alt="aoc_hat">
</div>

<div class="container">
    <h1 id="headline">Countdown to start the 2022 edition - (UTC-5)</h1>
    <div id="countdown">
        <ul>
            <li><span id="week"><%= @time[:week] %></span>weeks</li>
            <li><span id="days"><%= @time[:day] %></span>days</li>
            <li><span id="hours"><%= @time[:hours] %></span>Hours</li>
            <li><span id="minutes"> <%= @time[:minutes] %></span>Minutes</li>
            <li><span id="seconds"><%= @time[:seconds] %></span>Seconds</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<p>"Everyone should solve puzzles for fun".- Eric Wastl</p>

